Kakuyi mpata, pakamanyabu muakulu wa tshiena-Romain, bakatuadija kubenga tshiena-Portugal.
Bantu bavua bamanye muakulu wa Tshimputulukeshi bimpe bavua bitaba diakamue ne: Tshimputulukeshi tshivua pabuipi menemene ne tshiena Espagne ne kakuvua mushindu mukuabu wa kutshilonga to.
Lelu'eu, biamu bia kale ebi kabitu bitamba kukuata nabi bantu to, bidi anu mu nzubu ya dilamina bintu bia kale anyi mu tulasa.
Nansha mutuvua tuela meji ne: dipanga bululame kadivua mua kukebesha ntatu idi nayi bantu lelu, bu mudi ya bungi mu bimenga binene anyi mu tulasa tua bikadilu bimpe, bavua mua kudiangata ne mushinga mukese kupita mutudi tuangata lelu.
Telesikope ya matuku etu aa itu yambuluisha bikole bua kumona bimpe lupepele lua mu miaba ya kule.
Ditua dia bilongo bia cerisier, ditudi tubikila ne: hanani, ndituadije mu Japon mu bidimu bia 1200.
Badi bamba ne: mu ditunga dia Chine, bilongo bia pome ke bilongo bitambe buimpe.
Mu ditunga dia Japon, bavua benze Tshibilu tshia kumpala tshia Disanka dia Mitshi ya Cerisière kumpala kua mfumu wa ditunga bua mukalenge ne muanabu ne mukalenge.
Bakeluba batu ne tshimuenekelu tshimpe ne batu badilongolola bua kuluangana mvita nansha bobu babaluisha mushindu kayi.
Wewe muye kutangila budimi buimpe, bobu bakubenge bua kudia "mamuma a mupuya muimpe", wewe pebe kuena ubitabila to.
Singapour mmuaba muimpe wa kuendakana, ne udi mua kusumba tshianana tshianana tshianana tshionso tshiudi natshi dijinga.
Kadi bu mudi mutshi wa mangaya muikale ku Nord kua Équateur, udi ne luya lukole (matuku onso) ne luya lukese (mu bikondo bia mvula).
Tshitanda tshikuabu tshivua ku nord kua Hebelone, muaba uvuabu bajike bankambua ba mu Bible aba: Abalahama, Izaka ne Yakoba ne bakaji babu.
Bakajadika ne: bavua bapesha bantu ba mu Hebelone ne bena Yuda bavua basombele pabuipi nabu mu musoko wa Alaba bintu bia bungi.
Misulu ya mu ditunga edi ivua miaba mimpe ya kuikishila.
Tshilejilu, udi mua kuya kumona mazuwa a mâyi a Loire ne a Rhine anyi kuya kuendakana mu bimenga bimpe bia mu Danube anyi ku tshisabu tshia mâyi tshia Erie.
Bakabutula nzubu yonso ya mu njila ne njila ya bantu bavua bapuekele ne bavua kabayi ne bukole.
Nowele ke umue wa ku bibilu binene bia bena Kristo ne udi upetangana ne difesto dia diledibua dia Yezu.
Bisamba bia bungi bidi pabi kabiyi bia bena Kristo bidi bienza bibilu ebi mu matunga a bena Kristo ne a badi kabayi bena Kristo pa buloba bujima.
Bamue bantu batu bamba ne: mbimpe kushala mutabale butuku bua Pasaka bua kumona dibika dia bafue.
Tshilele etshi tshidi tshipetangana ne malongesha a bena Kristo, kadi ki ntshia kulambula muntu udi kayi muena Kristo mu tshikondo tshia Disanka anyi tshia Dibuikila dia mpekatu to.
Mu bitanda bia kale, bantu ba bungi bavua babenga kuenza Pasaka ne Nsabatu, ne bisumbu bia bantu bavua babenga kudisangisha mu musokoko bua kusekelela dibika dia Kristo.
Nyama yonso ivua mifike muaba eu kumpala ivua yendela pa mâyi, inyema anyi yenda anu pa mâyi.
Bua bule bua njila wa ku mukuna munene eu, nyama kayivua ne mushindu wa kuendakana to, nunku mpasu ke nyama umuepele wa mu Galapagos uvua udia bisonsa.
Katshia anu ku ntuadijilu, nyama ya bungi bu mudi mbuji, mpunda, mpasu, nzolo ne mbua ivua miledibue mu bidiila bia Galapagos.
Wewe muye mu tshitupa tshia buloba tshia Arctique anyi tshia Antarctique mu tshikondo tshia mashika makole, kuakumona ne: kudi butuku to.
Mpunga muimpe wa kumona bukenke bua ku Nord, bualu butoke ebu butu buenzeka mu mêba a bungi.
Bu mudi buloba buikale ne bantu bakese ne dinyanguka dia kapepe kakuyi bualu, mbimpe kukeba dîba dia kutangila mitoto.
Kudi midimu mikese ya bena Japon idi mifuanangane ne midimu ya bena ku Mputu.
Muaku wa tshiena Ebelu udibu bakudimune ne: "tshilamba tshia mudimu" udi umvuija "tshintu tshidibu bafuta muntu bua kuenza".
Mudimu mukole utu anu mukole, bantu ba bungi badi benza mudimu mukole, kadi kakuena muntu nansha umue udi mupangile tshintu to.
Bena mudimu bavua ne bua kulomba dianyisha dia mfumu wabu wa mudimu bua kubenga kuya ku mudimu, ne bavua ne bua kusumba bintu bia mfumu wabu kabayi bamulombe dianyisha to.
